data.description: Please schedule your showing appointment today! This stunning four bedroom home on Lawton's southwest side offers numerous appealing features. Recently updated with fresh paint, new carpet, and new flooring in the upstairs bath, the home exudes a modern feel. However, the true highlight lies in the kitchen, which has undergone a complete transformation. The old elements were removed and replaced with new cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, fixtures, tile flooring, and more. The primary bedroom, located on the ground floor, boasts a walk-in closet and an ensuite bath with a whirlpool tub. The two spacious upstairs bedrooms also feature walk-in closets, while a loft living area provides versatility as an office space. The main living area is enhanced by a cozy fireplace. Additionally, this remarkable property is conveniently situated just minutes away from the bustling 82nd St. shopping area.
